== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime ifatanije n’amasosiyete yo muri [[Nijeriya]] Ascend Studios, ku ya 19 Mata Imyidagaduro Virgo Sun Ltd na Lufodo Productions ikaba yari iyobowe n’umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Gana]], Shirley Frimpong-Manso <ref>POTATO POTAHTO - FILM AFRICA 2020 <nowiki>https://www.filmafrica.org</nowiki> › film-africa-events › potato-p...</ref>. Irerekana ibintu by'akajagari bibaho iyo abashakanye batanye bagumye hamwe murugo rwabashakanye, buri wese afata ubufasha bushimishije bwabahuje igitsina<ref>Potato Potahto (2017) - The Plum List <nowiki>https://theplumlist.com</nowiki> › potato-potahto-2017</ref>.  Iyi filime yafashwe mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri, ku bufatanye n’abatunganya amafilime yo muri [[Suwede]], [[Bufaransa|Abafaransa]], [[Bwongereza|Abongereza]], [[Nijeriya]] na [[Gana]]<ref>Award-winning Potato Potahto shot on the Sony FS7 - Screen ... <nowiki>https://www.screenafrica.com</nowiki> › film-tv-video-production</ref>. 

