== Kwakira ==
Ibirayi Potahto yakiriwe neza na rubanda, kubera intsinzi Shirley Frimpong-Manso yagezeho mbere<ref>Review of Potato Potahto - OC Ukeje & Joselyn Dumas - Tha ... <nowiki>https://tharevue.com</nowiki> › Blog</ref>. Filime yagaragaye 7.9 nabakoresha kuri Nollywood Reinvented<ref>Potato Potahto heads to cinemas in Nigeria, South Africa and ... <nowiki>https://www.screenafrica.com</nowiki> › 2017/11/21 › film › em...</ref>.  Ibirayi Potahto yabonye imyiyerekano mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Durban ndetse n’Iserukiramuco rya Filimi [[Bwongereza|ry’Abongereza]].<ref>Shirley Frimpong-Manso's 'Potato Potahto' to stream on Netflix ... <nowiki>https://www.theghanareport.com</nowiki> › shirley-frimpong-ma...</ref> Iyi filime kandi yagaragaye mu rwego rwo gutoranya iserukiramuco rya Filime [[Afurika]] kuva ku ya 27 Ukwakira kugeza 5 Ugushyingo. Ukuboza 2019, Potato Potahto yongewe kumugaragaro kurutonde rwa Netflix<ref>Shirley Frimpong-Manso's 'Potato Potahto' makes it to Netflix <nowiki>https://www.graphic.com.gh</nowiki> › Showbiz › Showbiz News</ref>.
